description: Mission Ready Solutions Inc. provides personal protective solutions to the global defense, security, and first-responder markets in Canada and the United States. the company operates through two segments Consulting and Manufacturer Representation; and Inspection, Cleaning, and Repair Services. It offers protective services gears. The company also distributes, fire, military, emergency, and law enforcement products. It serves the Department of Defense, law enforcement agencies, and private security companies. The company was formerly known as Mission Ready Services Inc. and changed its name to Mission Ready Solutions Inc. in June 2018. Mission Ready Solutions Inc. is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
